data.description: Uptown convenience and affordability is offered in this wondeful home!  4  bedrooms and 2 living spaces. This home has a great floor plan with many options. There is a designated dining room that has perfect flow to the kitchen, both rooms have porcelain tile with pretty designed thresholds.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinets & granite counter tops. Split floor plan with 3 bedrooms separated from the primary bedroom.  Mastercool upgrade in 2021 to keep cool.  Huge 215 sq ft sunroom NOT included in the total sq ft. Lovely custom covered space in the backyard with brick laid pavers making this a perfect entertaining spot! Front yard has a covered porch and it is walled in for privacy. Huge backyard with a pull through gate for easy backyard access! Tons of parking and so close to shopping
